20.3 Pricing and Surcharge Communication
The gift-wrap surcharge (PKR 150 for Signature Gold, PKR 200
for Festive Red, PKR 100 for Eco Kraft) is added to the order total
in real time as the user toggles options. The surcharge line item
appears in the order summary with the label 'Gift wrap (Signature
Gold)' — never just 'Additional fee' or 'Surcharge'. The total at the
bottom of the form (and on the Place Order button) updates
instantly. The handwritten note is free up to 200 characters;
longer notes would require a larger card and are out of scope for
the launch.
